               <msContents>
                  <summary>I) Tǝrgʷāme malʾǝkta Ṗāwlos ḫaba ʾayhud za-Yoḥannǝs ʾAfa Warq "Commentary
                     of John Chrysostom on the Epistle of Paul to the Hebrews" (fols.
                     2ra-156vb)
 I-1) Introduction (fols. 2ra-5ra)
 I-2) Table of contents
                     (fols. 5rc-6vb)
 I-3) The commentary [34 dǝrsānāt "homilies" and 34
                     tagśāṣāt "admonitions"] (fols. 8ra-156vb)
 
 Additiones 1-2.</summary>
                  <msItem xml:id="ms_i1">

                     <incipit>
                        <foreign xml:lang="en"/>
                     </incipit>
                     <explicit>
                        <foreign xml:lang="en"/>
                     </explicit>
                     <note/>
                  </msItem>
                  
                  <msItem xml:id="ms_i2">
                     <note>- Text I-3 ends with an embedded colophon of the work.</note>
                  </msItem>
               </msContents>
